  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<h1 class=\"size-32 is-title1-32 is-title-bold is-upper\">獵豹學子 鄭秉皓錄取 竹科實中科學班 FUC微積分 心得分享</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">微積分課程是獵豹開給中學資優生的大一先修課，彌補課綱所學不足，讓願意努力學習的孩子能學得深入。對大學理工科系學習及未來就業帶來極大幫助。</span></p>\n\n<div class=\"edit\">\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">此次多位九年級FUC微積分課程的同學考取科學班，獵豹剛考上科學班的同學們也選擇加入FUC微積分課程的學習。<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">明天 FUC微積分公開課</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">2023.05.28(日) AM10:00~11:30 青昀博士主講</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">（一）微積分基本定理</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">（二）微積分應用於AI的實例</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">歡迎參加!</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv xzsf02u x1s688f\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/1289383175347698/?__cft__[0]=AZWPizb0uw2VIdShvMvf5_oi1Uf2esvucV14Q16ms7ASQR7rYYz6Oqrr3Tv0X6wsINMI-aw0gXG89_hPgwe2RI8hjgdVth_9OpqTU0ogy2PdkhNzYdgz4b-l1P36SLMadb3G9-d7la3STtn7hwo2cqrU&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1289383175347698/</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">---</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">1.</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">台灣高中的微積分課程只介紹了多項式微積分。</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">對照歐美、日等先進國家甚至亞洲鄰近國家，台灣的內容明顯膚淺且貧乏，完全沒有提及：</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">三角、指對數、極座標的微積分，瑕積分。</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">級數的斂散判斷、誤差。</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">常微分方程。<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">獵豹的課程系統完整且內容豐富。</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">(半導體人才系列報導》「連台大新生的成績都往下掉！」新一代人才危機浮現，恐怕與108課綱有關？台大教授的教學第一線觀察</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1fey0fg\" href=\"https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/article/category/183015/post/202305020037/?fbclid=IwAR3d2aVD7nDEzJfmr1Eq1Mq-CUDHV-9HKQ58Cp3A1lD1pko-0jp_-7juKfM\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.businesstoday.com.tw/....../202305020037/......</a>)</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">(為什麼AI工程師需要微積分?</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">Why Do AI Engineers Need Calculus</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1fey0fg\" href=\"https://www.c-sharpcorner.com/article/why-do-ai-engineers-need-calculus2/?fbclid=IwAR3v85I9gq0Cu-BPj-h6WPaDjVT_AmEGDcdfVID5sPwMtGNfAPokiVkFMw8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.c-sharpcorner.com/....../why-do-ai....../......</a> )<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">2.</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">微積分是工程科學、理論科學、AI最重要的數學基礎。<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">3.</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">至少14位科學班新鮮人參與此課程。<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">4.</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">獵豹課程高過AP,IB微積分規格，並為大學微積分奠定紮實的基礎。<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">5.</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">物奧選手必備課程。<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">6.</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">拒絕錯誤的課綱走向，擺脫沈淪的命運！</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">建立堅實的數學能力，培養卓越的國際競爭力！</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">學好數學 成為AI的主人！！<br />\n&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><strong>台大.青昀博士</strong></span></div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">FUC微積分公開課</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">（一）微積分基本定理</div>\n\n<div dir=\"auto\">（二）微積分應用於AI的實例</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" spellcheck=\"false\"><img src=\"pic/elite/cheetah-elite-33-body-1.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
